# StockSage API — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your keys
#
# ── FREE (no keys needed) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#   Live prices ALL NSE stocks  → NSE India direct API
#   India VIX                   → NSE India direct API
#   D-1 snapshot                → SQLite (auto, built-in)
#
# ── ~$10/month — THE ONE KEY THAT FIXES EVERYTHING ───────────────────────────
#
#   RapidAPI Yahoo Finance (apidojo/yahoo-finance1)
#   Sign up: https://rapidapi.com/apidojo/api/yahoo-finance1
#
#   Fixes ALL of these:
#     ✅ Price history (charts, 1w/1m/3m/1y) for all NSE stocks
#     ✅ Technical indicators (RSI, MACD, EMA — computed from history)
#     ✅ Fundamentals (P/E, ROE, D/E, earnings, dividend yield)
#     ✅ Index history sparklines (NIFTY, SENSEX, BANK NIFTY, NIFTY IT)
#     ✅ Quarterly revenue & profit charts
#     ✅ Screener (needs history + fundamentals)
#     ✅ Non-NIFTY50 stock fundamentals (PAYTM, ZOMATO, etc.)
#
RAPIDAPI_KEY=your_rapidapi_key_here

# ── FREE — Twelve Data free plan ──────────────────────────────────────────────
#   Only for 3 macro tickers on the Sentiment page:
#   INR/USD rate, Brent crude, Gold (XAU/USD) — all on free plan
#   Sign up: https://twelvedata.com
#
TWELVEDATA_API_KEY=your_twelvedata_free_key_here

# ── Market news — free tier (100 req/day) ─────────────────────────────────────
#   Sign up: https://www.marketaux.com
MARKETAUX_API_KEY=your_marketaux_key_here

# ── Optional later — EODHD for richer fundamentals ────────────────────────────
#   $19.99/month if you need deeper fundamental data coverage
#   Only add this after verifying NSE coverage on their exchange list
# EODHD_API_KEY=your_eodhd_key_here
